</tr>

</table>

<hr>

<h3>Refund Management</h3>

<input type="text" placeholder="PNR Number">

<input type="number" placeholder="Refund Amount">

<button type="button" onclick="processRefund()">
Process Refund
</button>

</section>

<!-- ================= ABOUT ================= -->

<section id="about" class="page" style="display:none;">

<h2>About Railway Reservation System</h2>

<p>

The Railway Reservation System helps passengers search trains,
check seat availability, reserve tickets, cancel tickets,
check PNR status and print tickets.
It also provides an Admin Panel for managing train schedules,
fares, seat availability and passenger details.

</p>

</section>

